 Photo taken on Nov. 17, 2021 shows the scenery of earth forest in Yuanmou County, southwest China's Yunnan Province. The earth forest, which was formed by geological movement and soil erosion, is basically in color of yellow and the color varies in different parts. (Xinhua/Wang Guansen)  Photo taken on Nov. 17, 2021 shows the scenery of earth forest in Yuanmou County, southwest China's Yunnan Province. The earth forest, which was formed by geological movement and soil erosion, is basically in color of yellow and the color varies in different parts. (Xinhua/Wang Guansen)  Photo taken on Nov. 17, 2021 shows the scenery of earth forest in Yuanmou County, southwest China's Yunnan Province. The earth forest, which was formed by geological movement and soil erosion, is basically in color of yellow and the color varies in different parts. (Xinhua/Wang Guansen)  Photo taken on Nov. 17, 2021 shows the scenery of earth forest in Yuanmou County, southwest China's Yunnan Province. The earth forest, which was formed by geological movement and soil erosion, is basically in color of yellow and the color varies in different parts. (Xinhua/Wang Guansen)